sub_title: Senior Logistics Manager at SC Raw Materials
summary: I easily get along with colleagues, oriented work in a team, but can also solve and complete complex tasks alone. For many years I have successfully completed logistics tasks for the delivery of goods to Eastern Europe and Russia, well aware of the specifics of work in these countries. Speak Dutch (NT2-II), English and Russian
